**Negative evidence — what’s NOT there:**

Nine production services were checked. Zero read Universe deeply:

- services/episodeScriptWriterService.js — reads franchise_knowledge (FranchiseKnowledge.findAll where always_inject=true LIMIT 50 at line 169). Universe bypassed.

