- **CZ-29** — pnos_beliefs is the canonical authority for arc progression’s narrative-debt prose; never read. F-Lala-1 + F-Arc-14.

- **CZ-30** — world_rules and Show Bible rules are parallel rule systems. F-Lala-3 + Zone 14.

